# Implementation Plan - Content Momentum Engine

# Goal Description
Initialize and implement the "Content Momentum Engine" v1.0 based on [SRS.md](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/nexuslite/SRS.md). 
The system will allow users to ingest content (URL/Text/Image), process it via AI chains (Analyst -> Strategist -> Writer -> Editor), and manage drafts for multiple social platforms.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Architecture Decision**: We are using **Next.js (Frontend)** and **FastAPI (Backend)** as defined in the SRS. This requires running two servers during development.
> **Scraping Auth**: The user must provide `auth.json` (Playwright storage state) for LinkedIn/FB scraping to work. This file is not generated by the app; the user must generate it manually initially (or we can provide a helper script later).
> **CSS Strategy**: We will use **Tailwind CSS** as requested. We will use `npx create-next-app -y` with Tailwind pre-configured.

